  "TalkData": [
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "This is...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-adult01-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_notice_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_01_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(The magical girl-themed outfit...!)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute12-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_sparkling_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_02_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "...It's amazing.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute12-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_07",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_03_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(It's by the same creator as the one in the exhibition space... right. I thought this when I saw it earlier, too, but... you really feel drawn into its world.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-animal02-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_04_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(The model's scarred makeup, the bandages wrapped around her arms and legs... It really looks like she just got out of a battle.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute02-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_05_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Audience",
      "Body": "Eh, what's that? Looks painful~...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_06_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Audience",
      "Body": "It feels a bit scary, doesn't it...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_07_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Audience",
      "Body": "But the way the outfit is torn up is kind of cute. I wonder how they made it look so realistic?",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_08_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(...Why did they design an outfit like this, I wonder?)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-adult01-think",
          "FacialName": "face_smallmouth_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_09_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(The fact that they used the same motif for both the exhibit and the stage... means the designer must be incredibly passionate about it.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-adult01-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_serious_02",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_10_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(If people could look at the works I want to create like this...)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal03-relief",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_11_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "(I wonder how that would feel.)",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal03-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_07",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_12_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Phew~, that was so much fun!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_13_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Miku",
      "Body": "'There were so many different clothes, it was interesting.'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_14_21_night",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Right! I got so much inspiration from it, I'm really glad I came!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute02-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_15_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Miku",
      "Body": "'It looks like everyone is going home. Is the open campus over already?'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 303,
          "MotionName": "w-normal15-nod",
