      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Eh? Um...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal01-tiltheadB",
          "FacialName": "face_notice_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_47_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Woman A",
      "Body": "Jeez, they won't understand with just that. Why don't you explain it a bit more?",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_48_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "...But they probably don't want to listen to some stranger ramble on.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_49_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Ah... If you're willing to talk about it, I'd love to hear it!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-adult01-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_notice_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_50_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "That is, if it's not a bother...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute12-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_06",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_51_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "........",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 2,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_52_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "...I always thought magical girls were tragic existences.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_53_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "Like, they're always fighting enemies, right? And even when they get hurt, they never stop fighting.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_54_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "I know it's just a 2D story, but I used to wonder why they go to such lengths to fight.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_55_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "But... I realized I felt the same way.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_56_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Eh...?",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cool02-tiltheadB",
          "FacialName": "face_notice_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_57_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "...A long time ago, I used to make doll clothes for my little sister. People made fun of me for it, said all sorts of things.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_58_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "I told myself it didn't matter what a bunch of people who knew nothing said, that it was stupid, but it still pissed me off every time.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_59_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Ah...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-cute02-tilthead",
          "FacialName": "face_sad_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_60_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "But even so, to keep living, I still put on my uniform every day and went to school.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_61_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "I realized that I was just like the magical girls I used to think about.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_62_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "Even if you're hurt, in order to keep living, you have to keep going to places with people you hate and continue fighting.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_63_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "If that's the case—I wanted to express all of it through my clothes, wounds included.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_64_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Woman A",
      "Body": "And that's why he's always, *always* making clothes like this. I was so surprised when I first saw them~",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_65_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "Ah, um, but...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal15-shy",
          "FacialName": "face_worry_01",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_66_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Woman A",
      "Body": "But, I absolutely love his clothes!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_67_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Woman A",
      "Body": "If anything, I prefer Y2K fashion, so Lolita isn't really my style to begin with, but...",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_68_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Woman A",
      "Body": "When I first saw them, I was just overwhelmed. Like, every single scar had a backstory—I realized there's a worldview here that only he can create.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_69_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Woman B",
      "Body": "Hehe. Every time Yoshino made a piece, you'd always interrogate him like, 'Why did you express it like that!?' or 'What's the deal with that distressed detailing!?'",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_70_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "That was really annoying, actually.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_71_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Woman A",
      "Body": "Hey~!",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_72_9999",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 1,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Mizuki",
      "Body": "...You guys seem like you're having fun.",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "MotionName": "w-normal03-nod",
          "FacialName": "face_smile_07",
          "TimingSyncValue": 0.0
        }
      ],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 297,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_73_20",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
      "RequirePlayEffect": 0,
      "EffectReferenceIdx": 0,
      "RequirePlaySound": 0,
      "SoundReferenceIdx": 0,
      "TargetValueScale": 0.0
    },
    {
      "TalkCharacters": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0
        }
      ],
      "WindowDisplayName": "Yoshino",
      "Body": "Eh, does it look like that?",
      "TalkTention": 0,
      "LipSync": 1,
      "MotionChangeFrom": 1,
      "Motions": [],
      "Voices": [
        {
          "Character2dId": 0,
          "VoiceId": "voice_ev_night_25_04_74_1085",
          "Volume": 1.0
        }
      ],
      "Speed": 0.0,
      "FontSize": 0,
      "WhenFinishCloseWindow": 0,
